Angela Simmons’ ex fiancé and the father of her child, Sutton Tennyson, has passed away. According to TheShadeRoom, Tennyson was shot and killed on Sunday at his home. Simmons, Rev Run’s youngest daughter, began dating Tennyson in 2015 and the pair welcomed their baby, Sutton Jr., in September 2016. They would call off their engagement a year later with Simmons announcing it in an Instagram post.  